(7, 'content', 'App\\Models\\Berita', 7, '<div>&nbsp;Selasa, (06/02/2024) Kepala Dinas Pendidikan dan Kebudayaan Kota Malang Bapak Suwarjana, SE., MM menghadiri kegiatan Bimbingan Teknis Platform Merdeka Belajar (PMM) bagi guru Pendidikan Anak Usia Dini yang merupakan sub kegiatan Pengembangan Karir Pendidik dan Tenaga Kependidikan pada Satuan Pendidikan PAUD bertempat di Ascent Premiere Hotel and Convention Malang. <br><br><figure data-trix-attachment=\"{&quot;contentType&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;filename&quot;:&quot;news_17077296260.png&quot;,&quot;filesize&quot;:50823,&quot;height&quot;:508,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/WmuvrBknqFqTlSuk0LSbPbdgDpa61iYntHga3TbP.jpg&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/WmuvrBknqFqTlSuk0LSbPbdgDpa61iYntHga3TbP.jpg&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:1078}\" data-trix-content-type=\"image/png\" data-trix-attributes=\"{&quot;presentation&quot;:&quot;gallery&quot;}\" class=\"attachment attachment--preview attachment--png\"><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/WmuvrBknqFqTlSuk0LSbPbdgDpa61iYntHga3TbP.jpg\"><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/WmuvrBknqFqTlSuk0LSbPbdgDpa61iYntHga3TbP.jpg\" width=\"1078\" height=\"508\"><figcaption class=\"attachment__caption\"><span class=\"attachment__name\">news_17077296260.png</span> <span class=\"attachment__size\">49.63 KB</span></figcaption></a></figure></div>', '2024-08-13 19:24:07', '2024-08-13 19:24:07'),
